Eclipse SDK

Build id: M20050929-0840

I haven't been able to reproduce this with Eclipse 3.1.1.  This functionality was improved slight in tonight's 0.4.6 release.  Could you update and let me know if you still see any of these exceptions?  If so, let me know any other major features that you have installed, and when they happen (i.e. what kind of editor opening triggers them).  Thanks.
